---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';

const metadata = {
  title: 'Terms of Service - Siplinx AI',
  description: 'Terms and conditions governing your use of Siplinx AI desktop application and services.',
};

const lastUpdated = 'June 18, 2026';
---

<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <section class="relative not-prose overflow-hidden">
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 via-white to-violet-50 dark:from-[#06051A] dark:via-[#060512] dark:to-[#0A0618]"
    >
    </div>
    <div class="absolute orb orb-blue w-52 h-52 -top-10 -left-10"></div>
    <div class="absolute orb orb-violet w-44 h-44 -bottom-8 -right-8"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 text-center py-12 md:py-16">
      <p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 mb-4">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4" data-delay="80">
        Terms of Service
      </h1>
      <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm" data-delay="160">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
    <div
      class="prose prose-gray dark:prose-invert max-w-none prose-headings:font-bold prose-headings:tracking-tight prose-a:text-blue-600 dark:prose-a:text-blue-400"
    >
      <h2>1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
      <p>
        By downloading, installing, or using Siplinx AI ("the App", "the Software"), you agree to be bound by these
        Terms of Service ("Terms"). If you do not agree, do not use the Software.
      </p>
      <p>
        These Terms apply to all users of Siplinx AI, including individuals and organizations using the App under any
        subscription plan.
      </p>

      <h2>2. Description of Service</h2>
      <p>
        Siplinx AI is a desktop application that installs local AI models (LLM and STT) on your device to transcribe,
        summarize, and organize meeting notes. All AI processing happens on your device. Siplinx AI requires a valid
        subscription after the free trial period to continue operating.
      </p>

      <h2>3. License</h2>
      <p>
        Subject to your compliance with these Terms and payment of applicable fees, we grant you a limited,
        non-exclusive, non-transferable, revocable license to install and use one copy of Siplinx AI on the number of
        devices permitted by your subscription plan.
      </p>
      <p>You may not:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Copy, modify, or distribute the Software</li>
        <li>Reverse engineer, decompile, or disassemble the Software</li>
        <li>Sublicense, sell, or transfer the Software or any license key</li>
        <li>Use the Software to develop a competing product</li>
        <li>Remove or obscure any proprietary notices in the Software</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>4. Free Trial</h2>
      <p>
        Siplinx AI offers a free trial. No credit card is required to start the trial. At the end of the trial
        period, the App will stop functioning unless you activate a paid subscription. Trial accounts are limited to one
        trial per email address.
      </p>

      <h2>5. Subscription and Payment</h2>
      <p>
        Paid subscriptions are billed monthly or annually as selected at checkout. Payments are processed by Stripe. By
        subscribing, you authorize recurring charges to your payment method.
      </p>
      <p>
        All fees are non-refundable except where required by applicable law. We reserve the right to change subscription
        pricing with 30 days' notice to active subscribers.
      </p>

      <h2>6. Cancellation</h2>
      <p>
        You may cancel your subscription at any time from within the App (Settings → Subscription → Cancel Plan).
        Cancellation takes effect at the end of the current billing period. You will retain access to the App until
        then.
      </p>

      <h2>7. Acceptable Use</h2>
      <p>You agree to use Siplinx AI only for lawful purposes. You must not use the App to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Record conversations without the consent of all participants where required by law</li>
        <li>Violate any applicable privacy, wiretapping, or recording laws</li>
        <li>Infringe on intellectual property rights of others</li>
        <li>Interfere with the App's license enforcement or telemetry systems</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        <strong
          >You are solely responsible for ensuring that your use of Siplinx AI complies with all applicable laws in your
          jurisdiction, including any consent requirements for recording conversations.</strong
        >
      </p>

      <h2>8. Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p>
        Siplinx AI and all related software, trademarks, and content are owned by Siplinx AI or its licensors. These
        Terms do not grant you any rights in our intellectual property except the limited license described in Section
        3.
      </p>
      <p>
        Notes, transcripts, and summaries generated by the App using your meeting audio are your content. We make no
        claim to ownership of any content you create using Siplinx AI.
      </p>

      <h2>9. Privacy</h2>
      <p>
        Your use of Siplinx AI is subject to our <a href="/privacy/">Privacy Policy</a>, which is incorporated into these
        Terms by reference. The App processes all meeting content locally on your device.
      </p>

      <h2>10. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
      <p>
        SIPLINX AI IS PROVIDED "AS IS" AND "AS AVAILABLE" WITHOUT WARRANTIES OF ANY KIND, EXPRESS OR IMPLIED, INCLUDING
        BUT NOT LIMITED TO WARRANTIES OF MERCHANTABILITY, FITNESS FOR A PARTICULAR PURPOSE, AND NON-INFRINGEMENT. WE DO
        NOT WARRANT THAT THE APP WILL BE ERROR-FREE, ACCURATE, OR UNINTERRUPTED.
      </p>

      <h2>11. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>
        TO THE MAXIMUM EXTENT PERMITTED BY APPLICABLE LAW, SIPLINX AI AND ITS OFFICERS, EMPLOYEES, AND LICENSORS SHALL
        NOT BE LIABLE FOR ANY INDIRECT, INCIDENTAL, SPECIAL, CONSEQUENTIAL, OR PUNITIVE DAMAGES, INCLUDING LOSS OF
        PROFITS, DATA, OR GOODWILL, ARISING OUT OF OR IN CONNECTION WITH THESE TERMS OR YOUR USE OF THE SOFTWARE, EVEN
        IF WE HAVE BEEN ADVISED OF THE POSSIBILITY OF SUCH DAMAGES.
      </p>
      <p>
        OUR TOTAL LIABILITY TO YOU FOR ANY CLAIMS ARISING UNDER THESE TERMS SHALL NOT EXCEED THE AMOUNT YOU PAID US IN
        THE 12 MONTHS PRECEDING THE CLAIM.
      </p>

      <h2>12. Termination</h2>
      <p>
        We may suspend or terminate your license if you violate these Terms. Upon termination, your license to use the
        App ends immediately. Your locally stored notes are not deleted by us - they remain on your device.
      </p>

      <h2>13. Updates to the Software</h2>
      <p>
        We may release updates to the App, including updates to the local AI models. Updates may be applied
        automatically or require your action. Continued use of the App after an update constitutes acceptance of any
        changes to these Terms included with that update.
      </p>

      <h2>14. Governing Law</h2>
      <p>
        These Terms are governed by the laws of the applicable jurisdiction where Siplinx AI is registered. Any disputes
        shall be resolved through binding arbitration or in the courts of that jurisdiction, at our election.
      </p>

      <h2>15. Changes to These Terms</h2>
      <p>
        We may update these Terms from time to time. We will provide at least 7 days' notice of material changes via
        email or in-app notification. Your continued use of the App after the effective date constitutes acceptance of
        the updated Terms.
      </p>

      <h2>16. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        For questions about these Terms, contact us at <a href="mailto:support@siplinx.com">support@siplinx.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
